<p>
<font size="+2"><bold>Data and codes</bold></font>
</p>
<p><font size="-1">by Werley Cordeiro</font></p>
<li>
<b>Data</b>
</li>
<p>
Brazil Yield Curve <a href="http://www2.bmf.com.br/pages/portal/bmfbovespa/lumis/lum-taxas-referenciais-bmf-ptBR.asp" target="_blank">data</a>. Web scraping with <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Brazil_Yield_Curve/master/DI-Pre.R" target="_blank"> R function</a>.
</p>
<p>
Russian Yield Curve <a href="https://www.cbr.ru/eng/hd_base/zcyc_params/" target="_blank">data</a>. Web scraping with <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Russian-Government-Bond-Zero-Coupon-Yield-Curve/master/zcyc.R" target="_blank">R function</a>.
</p>
<li>
<b>Term structure models</b>
</li>
<p>
Dynamic Nelson-Siegel (DNS) model with <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Dynamic-Nelson-Siegel-and-Svensson/master/DNS-TS.R" target="_blank">R function</a> and <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Dynamic-Nelson-Siegel/master/DNS-TS.py" target="_blank">Py function</a>. (Ordinary Least Squares)
</p>
<p>
DNS model with <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Kalman-Filter-Dynamic-Nelson-Siegel-and-Svensson/master/DNS-baseline.R" target="_blank">R function</a> and <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Kalman-Filter-Dynamic-Nelson-Siegel/master/DNS_baseline.py" target="_blank">Py function</a>. (Kalman filter)
</p>
</html>
<li>
<b>Simple codes</b>
</li>
<p>
AR(p) <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/AR-p/master/AR(p).R" target="_blank">R code.</a>
</p>
<p>
MA(q) <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/MA-q/master/MA(q).R" target="_blank">R code.</a>
</p>
<li>
<b>Extra: Study materials</b>
</li>
<p>
Nelson-Siegel model <a href="https://docs.google.com/viewer?url=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Dynamic-Nelson-Siegel-and-Svensson/master/Nelson_Siegel_Math.pdf" target="_blank">derivation.</a>
</p>
<p>
R code <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/werleycordeiro/Durbin-Koopman-2012-Kalman-Filter/master/Durbin%20%26%20Koopman%20(2012)%20Kalman%20Filter.R" target="_blank">Durbin &amp; Koopman (2012) illustrations 2.2.5 &amp; 2.4.3 - P.16 e P.23</a>
</p>
<li>
<b>Mercado de Capitais</b>
</li>
<p>
<a href="https://htmlpreview.github.io/?https://github.com/werleycordeiro/Mercado/blob/master/CB.html" target="_blank">Conceitos básicos em R.</a>
</p>
<p>
<a href="https://htmlpreview.github.io/?https://github.com/werleycordeiro/Mercado/blob/master/CRRA.html" target="_blank">Função CRRA.</a>
</p>
<li>
<b>Q2 Quant FIA</b>
</li>
<p>
<p><a href="https://htmlpreview.github.io/?https://github.com/werleycordeiro/Mercado/blob/master/update_portf.html" target="_blank">Q2 Quant FIA Results</a></p>




